/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA persistence unit config\n- roster-boot/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml: CDI configuration\n- roster-boot/src/test/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/RequestBeanUnitTest.java: Updated unit test\n- roster-common/src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/request/Request.java: Interface (new package)\n- roster-common/src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/util/*.java: Utility classes (new package)\n- smoke.py: Comprehensive smoke test suite\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- roster-boot/src/main/java/spring/ (entire directory): Spring-specific code\n- roster-boot/src/test/java/spring/ (entire directory): Spring-specific tests\n- roster-common/src/main/java/spring/ (entire directory): Spring-specific code\n- roster-boot/src/main/resources/application.properties: Spring Boot config\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-16T21:45:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure - identified Spring Boot 3.1 multi-module project\n[2026-03-16T21:48:00Z] [info] Generated smoke.py with 5 test suites covering all REST endpoints\n[2026-03-16T21:50:00Z] [info] Updated all 3 pom.xml files for Jakarta EE 10 + Open Liberty\n[2026-03-16T21:53:00Z] [info] Restructured packages: spring.tutorial -> jakartaee.tutorial\n[2026-03-16T21:55:00Z] [info] Replaced Spring Data JPA with EntityManager JPQL queries\n[2026-03-16T21:57:00Z] [info] Replaced Spring MVC with JAX-RS resource\n[2026-03-16T21:58:00Z] [info] Replaced Spring @Service with CDI @ApplicationScoped\n[2026-03-16T22:00:00Z] [info] Created server.xml, persistence.xml, beans.xml\n[2026-03-16T22:02:00Z] [info] Updated Dockerfile for Open Liberty runtime\n[2026-03-16T22:05:00Z] [warning] Fixed apt-get -> dnf for RHEL-based Liberty image\n[2026-03-16T22:06:00Z] [warning] Fixed microdnf -> dnf\n[2026-03-16T22:07:00Z] [warning] Fixed H2 data source URL in server.xml\n[2026-03-16T22:08:00Z] [info] Rebuilt with --no-cache to clear stale build artifacts\n[2026-03-16T22:09:00Z] [info] Docker build succeeded - all modules compiled\n[2026-03-16T22:10:00Z] [info] Open Liberty server started successfully on port 8080\n[2026-03-16T22:11:00Z] [info] All 5 smoke test suites passed (0 failures)\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 0 critical errors, 3 warnings resolved during migration\n  - `apt-get` not available in UBI image -> switched to `dnf`\n  - `microdnf` not available -> switched to `dnf`  \n  - H2 datasource URL not passed correctly -> fixed `properties.generic` to `properties`\n- **Critical Issues:** None\n- **Manual Intervention Required:** None"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":558,"cache_read_input_tokens":133591,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":558,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1391},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3b591f7e-183a-4681-abab-4c3b92831289","uuid":"f4b77934-acd4-42dd-b84e-34c88da1f3b8"}
